{"article_id":"cafoKeDFsnMEogfe","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Latest On Iran Deal :","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Obama Says","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Deal Provides New Way Forward","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"The United States and five world powers have reached a historic agreement with Iran over its nuclear program .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"As we 've reported ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"the deal puts restrictions on Iran 's nuclear program","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"and also sets up an inspections regime","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"that aims to make sure","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"Iran is meeting its obligations .","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"In exchange , the U.S. and its European partners have agreed to drop tough sanctions ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"allowing Iran to sell more oil and rejoin international financial systems .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"We 've got a broad outline of the news at another post .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Here , we 'll keep up with all the updates","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"that emerge throughout the day .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Make sure to refresh this page for the latest :","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Update at 8:51 a.m . ET . :","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Will Fuel An Arms Race","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Republican Speaker of the House John Boehner issued a scathing rebuke of this deal ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"it is `` likely to fuel a nuclear arms race around the world .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"'' Like many other critics of the deal , Boehner said","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"that under the terms","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"announced today ,","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"Iran will still be allowed to enrich uranium ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"and the deal does not outright dismantle Iran 's nuclear facilities . `` At the outset of these talks , the Obama administration said","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"it would secure an agreement","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that affirmed","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Iran does not have a right","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"to enrich and permanently dismantles the infrastructure of its nuclear programs .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"It said","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that sanctions would not be lifted","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"until Iran met concrete , verifiable standards .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"if these terms were not met ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"the president promised","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"he would walk away . `` The American people and our allies were counting on President Obama to keep his word .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"Instead , the president has abandoned his own goals . ''","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Boehner concluded :","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"`` We will fight a bad deal","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"that is wrong for our national security and wrong for our country . ''","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Remember ,","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Congress will have two months","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"to review the deal .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"This statement appears to set up a tough legislative fight between the White House and a Congress","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"controlled by Republicans .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu has already expressed his displeasure about the deal .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"On Twitter , he said :","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"`` From the initial reports we can already conclude","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"that this agreement is a historic mistake . ''","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Netanyahu has been opposed to this deal","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"ever since the interim deal was signed in 2013 .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"The prime minister delivered a speech in front of the U.S. Congress","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"warning","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that the deal would guarantee Iran a nuclear weapon","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"because it does n't outright dismantle the country 's nuclear infrastructure .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Speaking from Vienna ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Secretary of State John Kerry echoed President Obama .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"`` This is the good deal","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"that we have sought , ''","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Kerry said .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"The bottom line ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Kerry said ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"is that this deal increases Iran 's so-called breakout time","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"- or the time","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"it could take Iran","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"to make enough material for a nuclear bomb .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"According to Kerry ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"once the agreement is implemented ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Iran 's breakout time goes from two to three months to one year or more .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"-- Allows Iran to enrich uranium but to no more than 3.67 percent ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"which is needed for civilian purposes","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"but is much lower","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"than what 's needed for a weapon .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"-- Iran has agreed to turn its Fordow facility ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"which is essentially an underground bunker ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"into a research facility","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"where Iranian and world scientists will work side by side .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"-- The Arak heavy-water reactor ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"which could have been capable of starting production on weapons-grade plutonium ,","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"will be rebuilt","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"using a design","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"approved by the international community .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"That design will make the production of weapons-grade plutonium impossible ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Kerry said .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Update at 7:17 a.m . ET :","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"An Opportunity For A New Direction","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"In a speech from the White House , President Obama said","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"that quite simply this deal keeps Iran from acquiring a nuclear weapon .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"According to Obama ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"the deal cuts off `` every pathway ''","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Iran has to get to a nuclear weapon .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"It also :","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"removes two-thirds of Iran 's centrifuges ;","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"includes a commitment from Iran","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"not to use its advance centrifuges for a decade ;","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"and limits Iran 's stockpile of enriched uranium and weapons-grade plutonium for 15 years .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"The deal also gives international inspectors","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"what Obama said","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"was 24/7 access to Iran 's nuclear facilities .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"`` That means this deal is not built on trust ;","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"it is built on verification , ''","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"Obama said .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"Not having a deal ,","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"Obama added ,","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"would actually allow Iran to inch closer toward attaining a nuclear weapon","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"and would make a military confrontation with Iran more likely .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"`` We give up nothing","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"by testing","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"whether or not this problem can be solved peacefully , ''","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"Obama said .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"The president said","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"his administration would brief Congress on all the details of the deal ,","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"but he warned","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"that it would `` irresponsible to walk away from this deal . ''","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"The agreement ,","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"Obama said ,","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"makes the region and world safer .","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"`` This deal offers an opportunity","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"to move in a new direction , ''","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"Obama said .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"`` We should seize it . ''","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"Announcing the deal in Vienna ,","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"Federica Mogherini , the high representative of the European Union for foreign affairs , said","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"the deal meant Iran accepted","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"that its nuclear program would remain `` exclusively peaceful ''","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"and that it would `` never seek to acquire a nuclear weapon . ''","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"`` We delivered on what the world was hoping for :","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"a shared commitment for peace , ''","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"She added :","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"`` What we are announcing today is not only a deal ;","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"it 's a good deal . ''","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"While the deal represents a breakthrough","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"- one","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"that leaves behind decades of animosity and years of tough negotiations and secret talks -","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"this is far from over ,","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"because the agreement still has to be approved by various world capitals .","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"President Obama is scheduled to speak at 7 a.m. in an effort","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"to begin trying to sell the deal to the American people and a recalcitrant Republican Congress ,","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"which has two months","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"to approve the deal .","depth":8}],"relat